They like franchises like Guardians of the Galaxy and have watched movies featuring Spider-Man, Iron Man, Captain America, and The Avengers. They also enjoyed the recent Joker movie, praising Joaquin Phoenix's performance. While they used to watch TMNT as a child, they are no longer as interested in it. The seeker also has a positive view on superhero mashups.
